text: Shehzana Anwar (born 21 August 1989 in Nairobi) is a female Kenyan recurve archer. She competed in the archery competition at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, where she was the Kenyan flagbearer. She was defeated by Ki Bo-bae of South Korea during the first round of the women's individual competition. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Kenyan female archers Category:Living people Category:1989 births Category:Archers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic archers of Kenya Category:Sportspeople from Nairobi
